com.att.research.xacml.std.datatypes

Class ISO8601Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.std.datatypes.ISO8601Date
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticString, IDateTime<ISO8601Date>, java.lang.Comparable<ISO8601Date>

    public class ISO8601Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDateTime<ISO8601Date>, java.lang.Comparable<ISO8601Date>, SemanticString
    ISO8601Date is a representation of an ISO8601 format date without a time component. NOTE: This is actually the extended specification for XACML3.0, not a strict ISO8601 date
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    Author:
    car
